said something to me, man.

1266
01:18:59,844 --> 01:19:01,596
Sorry.

1267
01:19:02,639 --> 01:19:04,307
Did she file a police report?

1268
01:19:04,516 --> 01:19:07,352
No. I sent it over
to the Parks Department.

1269
01:19:07,560 --> 01:19:09,896
