1283
01:20:10,206 --> 01:20:11,499
Give me your badge.

1284
01:20:11,708 --> 01:20:14,044
See, I hate dirty cops.

1285
01:20:16,212 --> 01:20:17,964
Green, wait.

1286
01:20:22,052 --> 01:20:24,137
Green, wait!
There is something I forgot.

1287
01:20:24,346 --> 01:20:26,139
