Green's been shot!

1291
01:21:02,384 --> 01:21:06,137
I'm in the alleyway behind
John R and Seven Mile!

1292
01:21:06,346 --> 01:21:09,975
Suspects are two young black males
heading east on foot!

1293
01:21:10,183 --> 01:21:12,811
