- I got an idea.
- What?

1309
01:22:38,730 --> 01:22:41,232
We'll take the rest of the money
from Mom's insurance,

1310
01:22:41,441 --> 01:22:43,568
pay Sweet to call off the dogs.

1311
01:22:43,777 --> 01:22:46,821
- He'll deal. He's a businessman.
