1312
01:22:47,030 --> 01:22:49,282
if it takes you longer to say it
than it does to think it up.

1313
01:22:49,491 --> 01:22:51,618
Yeah, Jerry.
Sweet will meet up with you,

1314
01:22:51,826 --> 01:22:53,370
take your money.

1315
01:22:53,578 --> 01:22:55,914
Won't be able to find your body
till the river thaws.

1316
01:22:56,456 --> 01:22:58,583
