- Today?

1329
01:23:48,591 --> 01:23:49,843
- Yeah.
- That's in three hours.

1330
01:23:50,051 --> 01:23:51,803
Well, we ain't got no choice!

1331
01:23:52,012 --> 01:23:54,556
Sweet's supposed to roll up on us
any minute now.

1332
01:23:54,764 --> 01:23:56,808
