1336
01:24:07,319 --> 01:24:09,195
We need to take Fowler out
before the meet.

1337
01:24:09,362 --> 01:24:11,448
We can't kill a cop
even if he is dirty.

1338
01:24:11,656 --> 01:24:15,201
He handed Ma to Sweet, okay?
He ain't walking away from this.

1339
01:24:27,797 --> 01:24:30,592
Make sure the hole's cut
when we get there.

1340
01:24:30,800 --> 01:24:33,219
Hey, come here.

1341
01:24:33,803 --> 01:24:36,765
- All right. I love you.
- Now, don't get shot.

1342
01:24:36,973 --> 01:24:38,308
- Don't shoot anyone either.
- Relax.

1343
01:24:38,516 --> 01:24:40,185
Unless you have to.

1344
01:24:40,727 --> 01:24:43,730
Come on, now.
You know I love you, don't you?

1345
01:24:47,233 --> 01:24:50,570
Y'all be good now.
And take care of Mommy, all right?

1346
01:24:56,451 --> 01:24:58,370
Be careful.

1347
01:24:58,870 --> 01:25:00,664
I will.

1348
01:25:01,539 --> 01:25:03,291
Bobby.

1349
01:25:08,338 --> 01:25:10,632
Look, I know I don't
know you that well,

1350
01:25:10,840 --> 01:25:14,719
but don't you let him get hurt.
You bring him back to me.

1351
01:25:15,095 --> 01:25:16,471
I will, Camille.

1352
01:25:17,639 --> 01:25:18,932
