for the spring.

1356
01:25:37,951 --> 01:25:40,328
Hey, man, I need a big favor.

1357
01:25:40,537 --> 01:25:44,582
I'll give you $20
and this whole box of Baby Ruths.

1358
01:25:48,503 --> 01:25:50,714
You see that house over there?

1359
01:26:03,059 --> 01:26:05,103
Not till we hear from Angel.

1360
01:26:22,579 --> 01:26:24,789
- What do you want?
- I'm selling candy to raise money

1361
01:26:24,998 --> 01:26:28,710
for my baseball team. We wanna
buy new uniforms and equip...

1362
01:26:28,918 --> 01:26:29,336
Thanks. Now get the hell out of here.

1363
01:26:29,336 --> 01:26:31,087
Thanks. Now get the hell out of here.

