without the call,

1370
01:26:51,399 --> 01:26:52,984
- so just calm down.
- What the fuck you...?

1371
01:26:53,860 --> 01:26:56,655
- Jerry!
- Just keep stalling him.

1372
01:26:56,863 --> 01:26:59,491
Hold... I'm grabbing my scarf, man.
I'll be there in a minute! Hold on.

1373
01:26:59,699 --> 01:27:01,409
- Angel?
- Hey, I got him.

1374
01:27:01,618 --> 01:27:03,578
- Is he out of the way?
- What, you wanna ask him?

1375
01:27:03,787 --> 01:27:06,498
- Let me hear his voice.
