1380
01:27:23,515 --> 01:27:26,643
- That's our money?
- Yeah.

1381
01:27:30,438 --> 01:27:31,564
- Hey, man, hey!
- Relax, relax.

1382
01:27:31,773 --> 01:27:34,734
- Hey, what is this, man? What is this?
- Relax, relax. Just relax.

1383
01:27:34,901 --> 01:27:38,738
