1387
01:27:54,587 --> 01:27:56,464
Yeah, all right.

1388
01:27:58,008 --> 01:27:59,259
What did he say?

1389
01:27:59,467 --> 01:28:03,555
He say, "Hurry the fuck up."
Then he hung up.

1390
01:28:06,725 --> 01:28:09,811
You'll never get the belt. Trust me.

1391
01:28:15,025 --> 01:28:16,776
People never think to go for the bag.

1392
01:28:16,985 --> 01:28:18,987
It's always the belt first
for some reason.

1393
01:28:19,195 --> 01:28:22,532
The bag has to be clear, though.
Black doesn't work.

1394
01:28:25,910 --> 01:28:27,203
Get up.

1395
01:28:27,829 --> 01:28:28,872
Get over there right now.

1396
01:28:29,080 --> 01:28:32,500
- He's gonna end up dead.
- Ma'am, ma'am, slow it down a gear.

1397
01:28:32,709 --> 01:28:35,879
