promote me to chief.

1421
01:31:02,442 --> 01:31:06,446
You're one of
the Mercer brothers, brother.

1422
01:31:06,655 --> 01:31:09,824
No cop in the world's gonna
believe your word over mine. Sorry.

1423
01:31:10,033 --> 01:31:12,452
You know what?
You're probably right.

1424
01:31:12,661 --> 01:31:15,455
Other than the ones
